Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.05,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.95,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to my uncle's farm and \Nhelp one of the cows give birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:14.39,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going all by myself, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.12,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,And once I'm done helping,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:21.76,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can go shopping in the city.\NMy mom gave me some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.71,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:27.71,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want? \NI'll buy you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:28.71,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.01,0:00:31.96,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something. I mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.86,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.57,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:41.83,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to buy you something \Nsince you've never been to the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:45.88,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just go to the city or wherever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:47.56,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:48.72,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:49.84,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:50.84,Flashback,Older sis,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.03,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:55.68,Flashback,Older sis,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.01,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,We're not fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.53,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.85,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:02.83,Flashback,Older sis,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.23,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:06.38,Flashback,Older sis,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:12.47,Flashback,Cow girl Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:13.40,Flashback,Cow girl uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:17.47,Flashback,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to keep pouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:20.41,Flashback,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you looking forward \Nto going to the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:23.28,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:28.11,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,But since he couldn't come,\NI wanted to buy him something,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:30.71,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,and then he got really angry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:33.96,Flashback,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he wanted to come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:35.28,Flashback,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Think about how he feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.45,0:01:38.09,Flashback,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Did you two make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:41.70,Flashback,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,You should, once you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:47.55,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to make up with him.\N I wanted to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:52.19,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,But saying "I'm sorry"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.60,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,is hard, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.02,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.61,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're an early riser, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:50.50,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.27,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a nice day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.64,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:55.69,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.18,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is my uncle already up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.07,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:03.45,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm pretty sure he'll be up soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.58,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:06.27,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:09.21,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get breakfast ready, \Nso let's eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.20,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:17.17,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,He always checks to see if there \Nare any footprints at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.17,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,The goblins move around at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.89,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,They return to their nests in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.90,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,but they always scout before attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:30.42,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,He told me that those are the \Nfootprints he's looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.90,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't find any footprints,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:38.61,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,he then carefully checks the fence to \Nsee if any part is loose or damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.39,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,If any parts are broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:45.46,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,he gets out some wood and a stake to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.37,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,This hasn't changed since \Nhe came here five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:51.26,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's his daily routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:55.38,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(276,1)}Goblin Slayer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.98,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.85,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,It smells great, as usual. Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.85,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.93,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:06.93,Main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:09.90,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.91,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's what I owe you for this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.59,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:20.57,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I guess being an adventurer \Nis pretty lucrative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:23.24,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I've had a lot of work lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:24.74,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:28.98,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Say, um... Are you going again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:32.87,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm going to the guild. \NThere's plenty of work there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.62,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:36.53,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:40.88,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I need to make some deliveries. \NWe should go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.76,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:45.90,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'll ready a wagon for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:49.68,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we'll be fine! \NYou're too protective, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.29,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stronger than I look, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.23,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to take over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.87,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:01.77,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.22,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:04.54,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.36,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,How are things lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.92,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,There are more goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.33,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.71,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Far more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.06,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:13.81,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.37,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,You do go out a lot more lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.25,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.47,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Having more work is a good thing, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.59,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:23.38,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.22,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's better when there are no goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:34.14,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.77,Main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta help me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:40.22,Main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,Li'l goblin critters done \Nshowed up in my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:44.40,Main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,They're gunna eat my cows an' burn my fields!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.73,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you need an extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:50.16,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please submit your form and payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.94,Main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes'm. I got 'em right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.23,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your form is filled out correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.79,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just confirm your payment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.63,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Two, four, eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.19,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it looks like it's all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:14.51,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,An adventurer will head out there for \Nthe extermination within a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:19.57,Main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that them li'l goblin \Ncritters rape women and eat 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:22.69,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,There have indeed been cases like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:37.38,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,Another goblin-slaying request? \NThat's the third one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:38.54,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,What's the pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:45.48,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to rule out \Nany experienced adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.82,Main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,Only newbies would...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.20,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,There is one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.04,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,who's always willing to take care of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:52.69,Main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:55.17,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:59.46,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get a signature \Nat the reception desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:00.43,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.81,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,So this troll was bearing down on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:09.22,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,but I swung at it like this and dodged \Nits attack just in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.78,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well done, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:15.66,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,I am very aware that \Ntrolls are powerful foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:19.16,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,I faced a troll with just a single spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:21.54,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think I'm amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:24.74,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. If you're feeling tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:27.05,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'd recommend a stamina potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.51,Main,spearman,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.01,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,The Goblin Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.37,Main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,That's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.39,Main,Lady 1,0000,0000,0000,,That's the weirdo who only accepts \Ngoblin-slaying quests, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.66,Main,Female knight,0000,0000,0000,,He's a silver rank, just like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:48.82,Main,Female knight,0000,0000,0000,,If all he hunts is weak monsters, who knows \Nif he can even handle bigger prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:51.15,Main,Female knight,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they'll let anyone \Nbe silver these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.78,Main,Heavy Swordsmant,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him be. We'll never \Nhave to deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:59.75,Main,Rookie Swordsman,0000,0000,0000,,Look at him. I've never \Nseen such filthy armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.21,Main,Rookie Mage,0000,0000,0000,,Even our equipment is better than his.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.17,Main,Rookie Cleric Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.02,Main,Rookie Cleric Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,He must be a newbie just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:09.53,Main,Rookie cleric warrior,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad if he heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:12.97,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.51,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to post all the \Nquests available this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.22,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.81,Main,Guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.49,Main,Guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,Is there one for dragon slaying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:24.48,Main,Guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,I need to gain some more experience \Npoints by doing heroic feats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.10,Main,Guy 5,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even try it. \NYou don't have the right equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.48,Main,Guy 5,0000,0000,0000,,Just settle for taking out some bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.82,Main,Guy 5,0000,0000,0000,,The pay isn't bad, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.99,0:09:32.94,Main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Quests for porcelain ranks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.92,Main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,don't pay very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.07,Main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to just clean ditches...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.73,Main,Apprentice cleric,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be too picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.65,Main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.58,Main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin slaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.87,Main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,That seems made for rookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:47.78,Main,Apprentice cleric,0000,0000,0000,,No way. You heard the Guild Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.17,Main,Apprentice cleric,0000,0000,0000,,We need to start with the sewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.47,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see! Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:54.25,Main,Heavy swordsman,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:10:00.17,Main,Female knight,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking this quest. Look somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.85,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,That's no way to talk to \Nthe best on the frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:10.33,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now, everyone. You mustn't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.32,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,So he's really not going \Nto look at the quests...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:20.23,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he did say that there's no need \Nto rush, since no one likes goblin-slaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.19,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.19,0:10:24.00,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:26.53,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,A-About the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:31.47,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I still think destroying a cave with \Nflammable liquid is going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.03,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,What's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.51,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's a far better option than \Nletting the goblins live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:39.13,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you think more about consequences?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.64,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,You might cause an avalanche doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.55,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The goblins are a bigger problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.17,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:48.86,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm trying to say is that \Nyou shouldn't think that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:49.77,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.30,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:53.90,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd formed a party with \Nsomeone about a month ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.99,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:11:01.09,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Also, couldn't we use something... \Ndifferent... to cover our scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:03.81,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what time we're attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:07.00,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,E-Either early morning or early evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.04,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tell me why.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:13.34,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Because early evening for goblins \Nis early morning for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:16.50,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. So during their afternoons, \Nor the middle of the night for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.05,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,they are the most guarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:21.30,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Next. What are the steps to approach them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:25.81,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if possible, light a \Nfire and smoke them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.06,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,because it's dangerous inside their nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.31,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.96,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The only time we enter a nest is when \Nthere's no other way, we don't have time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.25,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,or we're certain we can kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.59,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:38.82,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.45,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good morning, Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.95,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Goblins. Are there any quests?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:52.71,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, goblin-slaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:54.37,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,We have three quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.72,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,One is from a river village in the west,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:11:59.03,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,one is a small nest in the southern forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.09,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,and one... I guess you could call it an old fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:04.73,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mountain castle in \Nthe mountains to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:05.93,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They've settled there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:08.60,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and there have already \Nbeen some casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:13.10,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,The younger sister of the one who \Nput up the request was kidnapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:16.50,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,and a wandering adventurer who went \Nto find her hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.62,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for them, then. \NBut I can't let the goblins live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:22.18,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,If I take them out now, \Nthere shouldn't be further casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.82,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be counting on you, then, Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.17,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,One question. Did anyone else \Ntake a goblin-slaying quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:31.87,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a party of rookies accepted one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.27,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,They took the request from the river village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.49,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Rookies? What was their party like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:43.40,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,One warrior, one wizard, and one priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:45.71,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,They're all porcelain-ranked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:47.57,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Not a bad balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:51.11,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the three who were in the lobby \Nearlier, they won't be able to handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.16,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Even my party had four members...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:55.06,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,I explained that to them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.48,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave them alone! \NWe have to go save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.58,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:00.31,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.50,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to destroy the \Nmountain castle in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.69,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're just going to abandon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:07.58,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go save them, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:11.49,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,But that means you'll be facing \Na horde of goblins on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.44,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I've done that many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:17.64,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I can never get through to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.59,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.84,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.28,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:26.23,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:27.10,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.62,0:13:28.95,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful getting home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:45.61,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come back that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.57,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Or the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.96,Italics,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's still fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.65,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have a hard day \Ntomorrow if you stay up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.13,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll go to bed after \NI wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:32.78,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Think about how it would feel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:35.38,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,if your home was suddenly \Nattacked by monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:41.17,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if your home was suddenly \Nattacked by monsters one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:47.43,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They act as though they own the \Nplace and kill your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.26,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,kill your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.60,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,and plunder the rest of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:05.26,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Another example would be if \Nyour older sister was attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:09.32,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,tormented, made a plaything, then killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.20,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say that you witnessed \Nall this, from start to finish,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:17.17,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,in hiding as you held your breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.43,0:15:21.92,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:27.13,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You would take up weapons and do \Nwhatever you could to get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.89,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You would hunt them all down and attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:34.39,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You'd kill, kill, and kill even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:42.38,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there will be days \Nyou're successful and days you fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.79,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You'll try to figure out the \Nbest way to kill them next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.57,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You'll think about this for days and months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:55.13,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,You'll test every single idea you come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:58.95,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,As you continue to do that,\Nyou start to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:07.38,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,A kind moron will suggest that \Nyou let the children live,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:13.07,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,with a smug face, not realizing that \Nthese things will attack villages
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:15.31,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,and steal livestock to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.02,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Young, aspiring adventurers as well as
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:21.03,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,new, porcelain-ranked adventurers \Nwill confidently say,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:24.39,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,"I chased away a goblin that\Ncame to my village once!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.77,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,"They're weak." "They're easy to deal with."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:30.36,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,The goblin that the proud youth \Nof the village had chased away
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:34.20,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,was no more than a goblin that had been \Nsmoked out and was trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.91,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,This gives them confidence, \Nand they become adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:42.12,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the goblins that \Nsurvived and gained experience
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:44.86,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,become Wanderers and continue to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:48.88,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, the Wanderers become the \Nleaders or the bodyguards of nests.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.10,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.86,Italics,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I am, in turn, a goblin to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:05.84,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,He's one matter, but you need to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:09.59,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I let him stay here because he pays, \Nbut you shouldn't get involved with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:14.20,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I know you were childhood friends, \Nbut now matter how he was in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:19.26,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:25.00,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:27.71,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,You realize that, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.05,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.49,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.72,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,That makes five.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.43,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.93,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.89,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,O merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:49.08,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,please protect us, the weak, \Nwith the powers of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.15,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:03.89,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that you'd been \Ngranted a new miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:07.67,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,That's six.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:10.21,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, we took care \Nof them pretty quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:13.65,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,T-To think that I'd be using Protection,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:17.05,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,the new miracle the merciful Earth \NMother bestowed upon me, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:21.01,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,They might have a back door \Nor an alternate escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:22.41,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let down your guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:25.40,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed you could even think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:28.22,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Imagination is a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:30.17,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Those who lack it are first to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:34.60,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Like the ones who dove in before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:35.99,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.66,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Great Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.65,Italics,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,why did you bestow this miracle upon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:07.52,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Now we don't have to put out the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.55,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Once it goes out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.91,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to hunt down \Nany survivors and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.77,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let a single one survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.03,Flashback,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,People may call you a specialist \Nwho only hunts weaklings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:24.81,Flashback,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,but you are doing something \Nthat needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.12,Flashback,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please be more proud of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:30.66,Flashback,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,You're a silver-ranked adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.18,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,As I figured,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.72,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to act more like a silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:55.49,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:58.21,Main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to post all the \Nquests available this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.98,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:20.06,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:20.68,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:24.39,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.37,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to make you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:27.67,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.79,Main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you something extra delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:32.08,Main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.23,0:22:12.79,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,The Goblin Slayer swung swift and true,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:17.09,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,sending the goblins' heads into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:20.84,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,O, behold his blade blazing blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:25.60,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,tempered in true silver,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.60,0:22:30.38,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,never betraying its master.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:35.00,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the Goblin King's \Nreign came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:38.85,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,The rescued beautiful maiden \Nleans into our hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:41.44,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,However, he is the Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:46.63,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,He is sworn to wander the \Nland, never to settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:51.39,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,The princess reached out her \Nhand, but only grasped air.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:57.99,Main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, our hero continued \Non his way, never turning around.
